  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "X-Men: Wolverine's Rage is a side-scrolling video game designed for the Game Boy Color. The game's plot centres around Wolverine as he pursues Lady Deathstrike, Sabretooth, and Cyber.\n\nUpon discovering schematics that enable her to construct a weapon capable of melting Wolverine's adamantium skeleton, Lady Deathstrike resolves to proceed with the machine. Wolverine must undertake any necessary actions to locate her and prevent the impending threat.",
